---
// About section for JUSTIN.
---

<section id="about" class="py-32 bg-[#050505]" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:1">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:2">
    <div class="relative h-[600px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden reveal-v2 reveal-left" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:3">
      <img 
        crossorigin="anonymous"
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503202576495-16ceb9c52d05?auto=format&w=1200&q=80" 
        srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503202576495-16ceb9c52d05?auto=format&w=320&q=80 320w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503202576495-16ceb9c52d05?auto=format&w=480&q=80 480w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503202576495-16ceb9c52d05?auto=format&w=640&q=80 640w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503202576495-16ceb9c52d05?auto=format&w=768&q=80 768w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503202576495-16ceb9c52d05?auto=format&w=1024&q=80 1024w"
        sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 50vw"
        alt="Justin Phillips walking in office" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover filter grayscale brightness-75"
       data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:4" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:5"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="reveal-v2 reveal-right" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:6">
      <span class="overline-text mb-6 inline-block" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:7">THE ORIGIN STORY</span>
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tighter mb-8 leading-tight" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:8">
        Precision Meets<br/>Persuasion.
      </h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6 text-neutral-400 text-lg leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:9">
        <p data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:10">
          Justin began his career handling significant cash flow and customer experience in the casino industry alongside operations roles at The Ohio State University. He transitioned into aviation as a NetJets Account Manager, honing high-stakes client service skills by coordinating elite travel for executives and the U.S. Secret Service.
        </p>
        <p data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:11">
          Following a post-COVID career pivot, he brought this systems-driven precision to the Columbus new construction market. By combining a relentless 'go-giver' networking philosophy with the scaling power of AI and social media, he rapidly became a top 1% national producer with over $100 million in lifetime volume.
        </p>
        <p data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:12">
          Today, Justin's mission is to speak on global stages, sharing the exact playbooks he uses to operate at an 8-figure level and helping businesses scale by solving their most complex sales, consulting, and event problems.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-10" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:13">
        <a href="#timeline" class="text-white font-bold inline-flex items-center gap-2 group" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:14">
          View The Full Trajectory
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:15">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
